    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept, good-condition car that shows nicely overall and should make a solid, dependable driver. The body and paint present well, with only the kind of light cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect for its age, and the interior appears clean and cared for. It is not a mint example, but it has clearly been maintained and should appeal to someone looking for a nice, honest car they can enjoy without taking on a major project. Overall, buyers can expect a presentable, usable vehicle in good shape with normal signs of use.",
