      "description": "Usable, honest fair-condition vehicle that should serve well as basic transportation, but it is not a perfect car. Expect visible cosmetic wear, small blemishes, and general signs of age and use inside and out, along with the kind of minor needs and upkeep common in an older used vehicle. It presents respectably overall and is a practical option for someone looking for a reasonably priced car without expecting like-new condition.",
